      <title>阿联酋称美国必须利用与以色列的关系推动停火</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/uae-says-us-must-leverage-israel-ties-to-push-for-cease-fire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿联酋一位高级官员表示，美国必须“不回避”对以色列施加影响，并推动有可能蔓延至整个中东地区的冲突停火。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/uae-says-us-must-leverage-israel-ties-to-push-for-cease-fire</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 21:30:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默寻求在与特朗普的会晤中建立“个人关系”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/starmer-seeks-to-build-personal-relations-with-trump-meeting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默确认，计划于周四晚些时候与前总统唐纳德·特朗普会面，以“面对面”了解他，结束为期两天的纽约联合国大会之行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/starmer-seeks-to-build-personal-relations-with-trump-meeting</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Smartmatic 与 Newsmax 在审判前夕达成诽谤和解</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/smartmatic-and-newsmax-settle-defamation-case-on-eve-of-trial</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Smartmatic Corp. 已与 Newsmax Media Inc. 达成和解，后者指控这家投票技术公司在 2020 年总统大选中操纵了唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 的选举，并在陪审团审判开始前几天解决了此案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/smartmatic-and-newsmax-settle-defamation-case-on-eve-of-trial</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 19:39:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
